- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper proposes a new software framework for managing big data, which involves designing and implementing software components. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the design and implementation of a framework for managing big data, which involves developing efficient algorithms and data structures.
